h1. showCatalogueElement

Event broadcast on the [$rootScope|http://docs.angularjs.org/api/ng/service/$rootScope] when
 [catalogueElement|Angular Enhancers] show method is called. It passes the element
 to show as the second argument to handler function.


h2. Usage
Register the handler on the current scope or the [$rootScope|http://docs.angularjs.org/api/ng/service/$rootScope]
to listen to show request.

{code}
$scope.$on('showCatalogueElement', function(event, element) {
    // display the element by e.g. changing the current route
})
{code}
